 <p>Welcome to IFL Watches. Your privacy is crucial to us. This Privacy Policy outlines how we, along with our subsidiaries and affiliated companies, gather, use, and share information when you interact with our website or any other digital platforms associated with us.</p>
 <p><strong>Your Consent:</strong> By using our services, you agree to the terms outlined here regarding your information. If you don't agree with these terms, kindly refrain from using our services.</p>
