 <p>We sometimes share your information due to our integrated service platform. Here's a closer look:</p>
 <ul>
 <li><strong>Service Providers:</strong> We share with vendors and consultants who help us with tasks such as web hosting, delivery, marketing, and legal advice.</li>
 <li><strong>Public Sharing:</strong> If you post a review, it becomes public.</li>
 <li><strong>Legal Requirements:</strong> We disclose data if required by law or for security and protection reasons.</li>
 <li><strong>Business Transitions:</strong> In mergers or acquisitions, your data might be transferred.</li>
 <li><strong>Internal Sharing:</strong> Data is exchanged between IFLW, its affiliates, and partners.</li>
 <li><strong>Your Consent:</strong> With your permission, we might share specific data.</li>
 </ul>
 <p>Additionally, aggregated or non-identifying information might be shared for various purposes.</p>

